ActIndian Act
SubjectOchapowace no 71-132, Saskatchewan ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise of the power of Saskatchewan to take 10.94 hectares (27.03 acres) of lands in OCHAPOWACE INDIAN RESERVE NO. 71-132; and (2) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of these lands, for the purpose of constructing and operating a highway interchange at the junction of provincial Highway 1 and the Pilot Butte access road, a service road, and as a site for public utilities.
